snippet.title: Palworld | Early Access Release Date Announcement Trailer | Pocketpair
snippet.description:
Thank you for waiting.

Palworld, the latest open-world survival crafting game will be released in ”January 19, 2024 (Friday)".

Early access will start worldwide with a global release. This news was revealed alongside their latest trailer for the game.

👇Click here for Palworld's WishList
https://bit.ly/palworld2312

[Palworld HP]
https://www.pocketpair.jp/palworld

We will be preparing a lot of content on the road up to release.
We will also post shorts, gameplay and tutorials on our socials such as YouTube and Twitter, so please look forward to that content.

[Palnews Tutorial]
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BWdpAYXTeZQ&list=PLptNv_Fxn9ie2lCt0_VQuRcd9_hfT6Uf9&pp=gAQBiAQB

[Paldeck Playlist]
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLptNv_Fxn9idzsTRulWNmLYKWgKhqKI5s

Don't forget to  join the Discord community and follow us on Twitter!
👇
Discord Community
https://bit.ly/palworld_discord_sns

X
https://twitter.com/Palworld_EN

✨Palworld seeking content creators and streamers !✨
https://www.pocketpair.jp/palworld/for-influencer

#palworld
#pocketpair 
#steam
